{"tid":665741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[再見了，新世紀福音戰士] 日本「EVA 初號機」結束運行　1,200 名支持者目送最後一程","createTime":"2018-05-15T08:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T06:19:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1dea50458fc99020ca80978f8581d4adab312780","tid":665741,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2-techbang.pixfs.net/system/excerpt_images/56995/original/3c51bdd323db5b5699d617f77fc31936.jpg?1519619819\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-techbang.pixfs.net%2Fsystem%2Fexcerpt_images%2F56995%2Foriginal%2F3c51bdd323db5b5699d617f77fc31936.jpg%3F1519619819&h=da8a9d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以人氣動畫作品《新世紀福音戰士》（新世紀エヴァンゲリオン）為主題的山陽新幹線特別列車「500 TYPE EVA（タイプエヴァ）」於日前正式結束運行。約有 1,200 名鐵路愛好者及動畫迷在最後一班列車開出時，齊集新大阪站月台一同目送這部特別列車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/1-24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F1-24.jpg&h=fd26f044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現場有一名年僅 9 歲的小小鐵道迷與父親和妹妹一起專程來到新大阪，以自己的相機為列車拍下記錄照片。場內亦有在雨中踩了一個半小時單車，來到的高中生支持者。在月台上亦有支持者扮演成劇中的女性角色，為特別列車送行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【有片睇】日本 EVA 新幹線結束運行　1,200 名支持者目送最後一程<br />\n讚好此文:<br />\n<br />\n五月 14, 2018 &bull;旅遊 &bull;<br />\n<br />\n以人氣動畫作品《新世紀福音戰士》（新世紀エヴァンゲリオン）為主題的山陽新幹線特別列車「500 TYPE EVA（タイプエヴァ）」於日前正式結束運行。約有 1,200 名鐵路愛好者及動畫迷在最後一班列車開出時，齊集新大阪站月台一同目送這部特別列車。<br />\n<br />\n現場有一名年僅 9 歲的小小鐵道迷與父親和妹妹一起專程來到新大阪，以自己的相機為列車拍下記錄照片。場內亦有在雨中踩了一個半小時單車，來到的高中生支持者。在月台上亦有支持者扮演成劇中的女性角色，為特別列車送行。<br />\n<br />\nEVA新幹線為記念山陽新幹線開通40 周年以及《新世紀福音戰士》動畫開播 20 周年，自 2015 年 11 月開始推出。特別列車以動畫主角乘坐的兵器「Eva 初號機」為主題，每日來回九州博多及新大阪。據官方表示，有關特別列車將會改裝成 Hello Kitty 特別列車，並預計在今年夏季以「Kitty 新幹線」名義運行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/05/14/eva-train-end/life-tech/travel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2Feva-train-end%2Flife-tech%2Ftravel%2F&d=BRltTxiy%2FjBf63PtM8VK2P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4578cf6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/05/14/eva-train-end/life-tech/travel/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7nDQhjqUNDI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7nDQhjqUNDI&d=BRltTxiy%2FjBf63PtM8VK2P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=092bfbd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7nDQhjqUNDI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f80ad6a3e75cc78f8211869de8351fb6213fac2","tid":665741,"uid":48064,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:29:45.000Z","msg":"呢款新幹線型到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351f9b9a4c9d11e8b1003e8e4f7017809bcf96dc","tid":665741,"uid":182315,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1f80ad6a3e75cc78f8211869de8351fb6213fac2","tid":665741,"uid":48064,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:29:45.000Z","msg":"呢款新幹線型到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:54:04.000Z","msg":"個design 真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a598933089095ceb799a29706818184e7b015fbc","tid":665741,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:29:10.000Z","msg":"有冇班毒撚鐵膠嘅相睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b9fa27e07a153f60e1529c6d44fb91d94555c6","tid":665741,"uid":35101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:51:43.000Z","msg":"好型<br />\n可惜無得搭lu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" cla